name: The bicycle thief
description: Took this picture a few years ago, when I saw the painted arm on that wall made by someone unknown I had to take one of the nearest bikes and put it as well in the image. I immediately got the idea of the image title: The bicycle thief. This images on HEN are part of my daily 10 project, 1 image each day for free in an 10/10 edition. Uncollected pieces are burned the next day.
